Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}后悔也完全完全完全无法释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:14.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}独自不断的钻着牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}成为不了完全的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}理想总是事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:24.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只准备好自责的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:28.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}寻求着那廉价的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:31.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论失败几次都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:34.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}虚心接受屡教不改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}昧着良心得过且过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有尽头的忏悔与忧郁的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有完美的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:56.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只有最差劲的自己
Comment: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,========================ED==================================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:08.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}始まりはただの恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}気づけば唯一無二の拠り所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}同じ時刻み　齢をとろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}これからは　お願いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}so long time 隣りにいて　永久に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}闘いの日々に疲れても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}怒りの雨に降られても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}濡れてしまうならば迷わず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}俺が代わりにあなたの傘となる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}寒くないよ　隣にいる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}ただそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}その笑顔にまた癒やされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}世界中　探しても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}代わりなんていない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:57.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}そこにいるだけでまた満たされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}どんなに傷ついても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:03.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}この身捧げ守るから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:08.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}最初不过是单纯的小小恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不觉间却成了我唯一的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}让我们在岁月中一同刻下年华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}今后也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}so long time 永远在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不论是历战的疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}还是暴风雨的侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}当你脆弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我将毫不犹豫地为你遮风挡雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}只要你在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就不会感到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}总能被你的微笑治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就算寻遍整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}也没有谁能代替你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:57.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}在你身边就是我最大的满足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不管受怎样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:03.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我都将舍身相护
